data.description: This charming 2-3 bedroom house offers a unique opportunity to embrace the comforts of home. The main floor boasts a full bathroom, a delightful half bath conveniently located near the bedrooms, and a surprise bonus room that can serve as a non-traditional 4th bedroom, office, or cozy den.   As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that radiates warmth and charm. With ample space for your furnishings and personal touches, you'll find it effortless to make this room your own.  An added bonus of this property is the ample off-street parking in the back. New furnace!
